ORGANISERS of the Klausified Music Contest have made an official announcement for talented artistes for the contest. The press released by the management, reads: any interested candidates can start applying to be part of the contest in order to stand a chance to win exciting prizes and other incentives. According to one of the organisers, Diamond Nicholas, the winner will win a million Naira and at the same time be contracted to work with one of the A-list producers in the country. “We will also promote our winner for a year across the country and beyond the shores of Nigeria. That aside, we also have a cash prize of N500,000 put in place for who takes the second position and N350,000 for who takes the third position.” He assured that the contest is not only about rewarding talents with money, but mentoring them to make their dreams realities.